led integer lag plot, which characterizes and distinguishes the ECG signals\nof NHP and CHFP, is finally obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Sep 2014 19:16:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2015 10:34:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-19"}
