istinct solution for the interval of $\\lambda_{b1}\\leq\n\\lambda \\leq \\lambda_{b2}$ and five distinct solutions for $\\lambda_{b2}\\leq\n\\lambda \\leq 300$. Also two transitions are observed in the higher energy\nbranch of the first bifurcation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Sep 2014 03:06:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Oct 2014 06:15:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Dec 2014 07:47:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-12"}
