 coefficients in\nPb+Pb collisions at $\\sqrt{s_{\\mathrm{NN}}} =2.76$ TeV with similar event\nmultiplicities. Reasonable agreement is observed after accounting for the\ndifference in the average $p_{\\rm T}$ of particles produced in the two\ncollision systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Sep 2014 13:40:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-08"}
