A with respect to its predecessors will\nallow to unambiguously discern which progenitor scenario (single-degenerate vs.\ndouble-degenerate) applies to them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Sep 2014 14:50:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Feb 2015 11:37:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-05"}
